metadata.name: “Te quería” I loved you #1/35
metadata.description:
**Te quería " I loved you. "**


This scene is a mystery, could it be a story of love and heartbreak, a crime, a tragedy, or nothing at all?

" Te quería" is an illustration that recreates a situation between two characters and various symbolic elements of great narrative power, where the color red predominates, adding a dramatic and vibrant atmosphere to the piece.

The work invites the viewer to create their own narrative that probably has a lot to do with their particular way of perceiving reality.  In the exercise of interpretation, each one assumes the facts according to their way of seeing the world.
